com.facebook.litho.drawable

Class ComparableDrawableWrapper

  • java.lang.Object
    • Drawable
      • com.facebook.litho.drawable.ComparableDrawableWrapper
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ComparableDrawable

    public abstract class ComparableDrawableWrapper
extends Drawable
implements ComparableDrawable
    Comparable Drawable Wrapper delegates all calls to its wrapped Drawable.

    The wrapped Drawable must be fully released from any View before wrapping, otherwise internal Drawable.Callback may be dropped.
